edict. Meter-scale variation in reef microhabitats affected {\textless}i{\textgreater}Symbiodinium{\textless}/i{\textgreater} communities in {\textless}i{\textgreater}O.{\&}{\#}xa0;annularis{\textless}/i{\textgreater}, and host genotype coupled with variation in {\textless}i{\textgreater}Symbiodinium{\textless}/i{\textgreater} communities appeared to mediate colony success. },
